{"tid":389554,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來我還想念你","createTime":"2017-09-06T10:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T22:53:06.000Z","uid":130591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7b9aac12301347bc9cc50d35f3dcf3d91255fa6","tid":389554,"uid":130591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T10:53:46.000Z","msg":"每當自己一人獨處之時，<br />\n你的身影總會在腦海浮現<br />\n<br />\n走在你曾走過的路上，<br />\n眼角總閃過你的腳踪<br />\n<br />\n知道你近來病了，<br />\n不知你身體安好？新環境適應嗎？<br />\n<br />\n早知今日，我便自私的不讓你走<br />\n但坦率的我卻為了準備大量信封和郵票<br />\n<br />\n因為，當時的我只想到要取悅你<br />\n想在你心中留下印記<br />\n<br />\n我後悔了! 怕且以後再沒有時間早午餐也撑枱腳<br />\n以後再沒有機會傾到不捨說再見<br />\n<br />\n或許我們根本不應相識，這明顯是緣分的作弄<br />\n白白浪費了你眼裡的秋波，我心中的思慕<br />\n<br />\n祝福你跟丈夫子女幸福美滿<br />\n也願我家庭和樂健康快活<br />\n<br />\n就此告終<br />\n恨愛成空<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c149a7df7d48b7a3bc356c8669f9f280001157","tid":389554,"uid":14217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeec94406548d4c1be1478405f07e534e54f8ef3","tid":389554,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T11:24:38.000Z","msg":"我沒有很想你 只是每早醒來第一個想到你"},{"pid":"e1f17dcf5b82a90d5cc09775ced752bdbfe5b775","tid":389554,"uid":130591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T12:36:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我沒有很想你 只是每早醒來第一個想到你</blockquote><br />\n已經夠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f815f1c9d60b7f1c16504ea32aeb1f967cbfb79a","tid":389554,"uid":130591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T12:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae6d3af9f9872381d8281002ec8431bb13ff19b","tid":389554,"uid":130591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T13:01:58.000Z","msg":"為何永遠放不低<br />\n<br />\n為何錯愛這一位<br />\n<br />\n但求仍然維繫<br />\n<br />\n不惜一切<br />\n<br />\n我為你執迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec25b72fe33ec4bcf7116737aae045d375b4e5d","tid":389554,"uid":141706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T13:08:08.000Z","msg":"放棄愛情"},{"pid":"5baa82e2da437d4e246ee8f3c9d65ceed1ffe7fe","tid":389554,"uid":130342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T13:09:18.000Z","msg":"你不會有家庭的 別想得太美好"},{"pid":"8a1c6e6c1e0ec1787fccc176e58c436b7c2809b3","tid":389554,"uid":102769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T14:14:37.000Z","msg":"有些時候 我會做夢<br />\n盼望 回過頭你在身後<br />\n沒有不快樂 沒有迫我做選擇<br />\n懂我拼什麼<br />\n懂我最寶貝你了"},{"pid":"5505473b7b1fe348bf84c38bd704b3435fbf78c3","tid":389554,"uid":80580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:02:57.000Z","msg":"我話過等你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b6878e2318f0ddbdf76aa053a6388182a50547","tid":389554,"uid":130591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:49:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你不會有家庭的 別想得太美好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n為甚麼？"},{"pid":"007605437b156f9dd28525751fa592fcdf616691","tid":389554,"uid":130591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:52:36.000Z","msg":"假如我是一朵雪花,<br />\n翩翩的在半空裡瀟灑,<br />\n我一定認清我的方向--<br />\n飛颺,飛颺,飛颺,<br />\n這地面上有我的方向.<br />\n<br />\n不去那冷漠的幽谷,<br />\n不去那淒清的山麓,<br />\n也不上荒街去惆悵--<br />\n飛颺,飛颺,飛颺,<br />\n你看我在我的方向!<br />\n<br />\n在半空裡娟娟的飛舞,<br />\n認明了那清幽的住處,<br />\n等著她來花園裡探望--<br />\n啊,她身上有硃砂梅的清香!<br />\n<br />\n那時我憑藉我的身輕,<br />\n盈盈的,沾住了她的衣襟,<br />\n貼近她柔波似的心胸--<br />\n消溶,消溶,消溶,<br />\n溶入了她柔波似的心胸!"},{"pid":"9eac8a39d0df500a54d8bb9363238e952a66d089","tid":389554,"uid":130591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T16:09:48.000Z","msg":"我是天空裡的一片雲<br />\n<br />\n偶然投映在你的波心"},{"pid":"699eedd063d7b7b16b1c5336f78e6f88bd8642ea","tid":389554,"uid":130342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T18:06:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你不會有家庭的 別想得太美好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n為甚麼？</blockquote><br />\n人生只有無限錯折 不會有順境的"},{"pid":"5ae6d7a5753eb0e4cd7f670af5930fb1d9bfe474","tid":389554,"uid":130591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:04:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你不會有家庭的 別想得太美好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n為甚麼？</blockquote><br />\n人生只有無限錯折 不會有順境的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實，我和她是真的有家庭的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85bba3b9cd9ad40a06118088f400ba8107e693c1","tid":389554,"uid":130342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T16:19:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你不會有家庭的 別想得太美好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n為甚麼？</blockquote><br />\n人生只有無限錯折 不會有順境的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實，我和她是真的有家庭的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想太多對身體不好"},{"pid":"384a89a3a39b5acc679d9bab09693f8cdc284cc2","tid":389554,"uid":102769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T06:52:13.000Z","msg":"原來愛情來過半分鐘也沒有"},{"pid":"3e4be146b9a1f9e6202fc994e94c88f468628eb0","tid":389554,"uid":130591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T10:35:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來愛情來過半分鐘也沒有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78804d3e3288518a2e3b01c846bd467336895c9","tid":389554,"uid":130591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T22:53:06.000Z","msg":"飛天遁地<br />\n貪一刻的樂極忘形<br />\n很想說謊<br />\n不眨眼睛<br />\n這愛情無人性"}]}